# Run Tests Before Done

After making code changes, run all tests with `make test` and ensure they pass before finishing.

## Requirements

- Run `make test` after any source or test file change.
- If any test fails, fix the failure before moving on.
- Do not consider a task complete until `make test` exits with zero failures.
- When a fix causes a new failure, iterate until the full suite is green.
